"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">1</A>
Publius Cornelius Scipio Africanus the elder had brought the Second Punic War to a close by defeating the Carthaginians at Zama in 202 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> The younger Scipio had destroyed Carthage in 146.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


