"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">2</A>
The war with Viriathus had already begun in 148 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> It ended in 140 by the treacherous murder of Viriathus.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


