onMouseOut="nd();">3</A>
Quintus Pompeius was consul in 141 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> In the next year he was forced to make the treaty with the enemy which the senate refused to ratify.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


