82 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>



	<HR CLASS="endnotes"><A ID="endnotes_T"></A>
	<H2>
Thayer's Note:
	</H2>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note:500_acres" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Velleius_Paterculus/2A*.html#ref:500_acres
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">a</A>
A very loose translation of the Latin text: 500 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">jugera</SPAN> was about 310 acres (124 hectares).



